<div class="patternContent"><div class="patternTopic"> <h1><a name="OSG_Security_Policies_and_Proced"></a>  <strong>OSG Security Policies and Procedures</strong> </h1>
<p />
<div class="twikiToc"> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#About_this_document"> About this document</a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#OSG_Security_Policies"> OSG Security Policies</a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Approved_Security_Policies"> Approved Security Policies</a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Security_Procedures"> Security Procedures</a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#References_and_Related_Informati"> References and Related Information</a> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#JSPG"> JSPG</a>
